OL,6,Fhave failed in their bid to appeal a
OL,7,Ffour point deduction for breaching the
OL,8,FPremier League's profitability and
OL,9,Fsustainability rules (PSR).
OL,11,FForest were originally handed a four
OL,12,Fpoint deduction for overspending.
OL,14,FThe news comes as Forest sit in 17th
OL,15,Fin the table, three points ahead of
OL,16,Fthe relegation places with two games
OL,17,Fagainst Chelsea and Burnley still to
OL,18,Fplay.
