OL,3,CNottingham Forest's appeal against
OL,4,Cfour-point deduction rejected
OL,6,FHowever, an appeal board announced on
OL,7,FTuesday that the original commission
OL,8,Fwas "entitled and right" to reach the
OL,9,Fdecision it did, and took aim at the
OL,10,Fapproach taken to the appeal by Forest.
OL,12,F"Some of the criticisms of the
OL,13,F(original) decision have involved a
OL,14,Fminute examination of the words used
OL,15,Fby the commission," the appeal board
OL,16,Fsaid.
