OL,6,F"Decisions such as these should not be
OL,7,Fsubjected to microscopic forensic
OL,8,Fexamination and interpreted as if they
OL,9,Fwere statutes which have been drafted
OL,10,Fby Parliamentary Counsel.
OL,12,F"Allegations of infelicities of
OL,13,Flanguage or errors which are not
OL,14,Fmaterial to the ultimate decision add
OL,15,Fto the complexity and costs of
OL,16,Fproceedings and are rarely likely to
OL,17,Flead to a successful challenge of a
OL,18,Fdecision."
