OL,3,CNottingham Forest's appeal against
OL,4,Cfour-point deduction rejected
OL,6,FForest were charged with overspending,
OL,7,Fwith 42 players arriving at the City
OL,8,FGround and more than #250 million
OL,9,Fspent since their return to the
OL,10,Fpremier league.
OL,12,FPremier League clubs are allowed to
OL,13,Flose #105 million over a three year
OL,14,Fperiod. However, Forest's permitted
OL,15,Flosses were limited to #61 million
OL,16,Fbecause they spent two years of that
OL,17,Fperiod in the championship.
OL,19,FHowever, Forest went over that #61
OL,20,Fmillion limit by #34.5 million.
